com.neovisionaries.bluetooth.ble.advertising

Class UUIDs

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neovisionaries.bluetooth.ble.advertising.ADStructure
      • com.neovisionaries.bluetooth.ble.advertising.UUIDs
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class UUIDs
extends ADStructure
    An AD structure that contains a list of UUIDs.

    This class covers the following data types. See Generic Access Profile (GAP) for the official list of data types.

    Data Type Value Data Type Name
    0x02 Incomplete List of 16-bit Service Class UUIDs
    0x03 Complete List of 16-bit Service Class UUIDs
    0x04 Incomplete List of 32-bit Service Class UUIDs
    0x05 Complete List of 32-bit Service Class UUIDs
    0x06 Incomplete List of 128-bit Service Class UUIDs
    0x07 Complete List of 128-bit Service Class UUIDs
    0x14 List of 16-bit Service Solicitation UUIDs
    0x15 List of 128-bit Service Solicitation UUIDs
    0x1F List of 32-bit Service Solicitation UUIDs

    This class was renamed from ADUUIDs to UUIDs when the version was upgraded to 1.4.

    Since:
    1.1
    See Also:
    Generic Access Profile (GAP), Serialized Form
